data.title: Valerie van der Graaf
data.text:
Search Valerie van der Graaf on Amazon.

Valerie van der Graaf (born 12 February 1992 in Rotterdam, Zuid-Holland, Netherlands) is a Dutch model who has appeared in Vogue, Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue,[1] and Playboy.[2]

Early life and discovery[edit]

Van der Graaf was discovered on the Dutch social media site Hyves at age 15.[1] She was sent a private message and she and her mother followed up.

Career[edit]

She was the cover model of the 2012 Lavazza calendar, and appeared in the 2014 Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue.[1][3] In 2016, she was the Playboy Playmate of the Month for August 2016.[2]
